# Security Phase 2 Scope (Local)

Date: 2026-01-18

## In scope

- Immutable backup agent (local + optional S3 Object Lock upload).
- Docker compose wiring for backup service and volumes.
- Secrets management wiring (Docker secrets + backend config fallback).
- Network segmentation adjustments in `docker-compose.yml`.
- Update `docs/ports.md` to reflect secret-based DB config and backup agent.
- Local backup copies of edited files (stored in `docs/archive/`).

## Not in scope

- No new external ports.
- No schema or migration changes.
- No frontend UI changes.
- No monitoring/analytics refactors.
- No data migrations or backfills.
- No external file transfer systems (local copies only).
